Test Scenario: Login functionality of a website
Test case ID:001
steps:
1.Go to website.
2.Enter valid username.
3.Enter valid password.
4.click on login
Expected result: User should login successfully and redirected to the Dashboard page.
Test Case ID:002
Steps:
1.Go to website.
2.Enter an invalid username.
3.Enter valid password.
4.Click on login.
Expected result:1.Appropriate error message should be displayed.
2.User should be on same page.
